We’re celebrating #WorldCocktailDay with a MIN8® by @sonjijam of Palermo’s @13_bootleg. Featured in @50bestbars #PassTheShaker series, this highball twist provides the perfect refreshment for a spring evening.

MIN8®
50 ml Michter's US*1 Bourbon
15 ml Mancino Red Vermouth
1 dash bitters
Chinotto
Build in the glass (highball). Fill with chinotto. Stir. Garnish with orange zest.

#WorldCocktailDay #PassTheShaker #Worlds50BestBars #50BestBars #MakeItMichters #Michters #MichtersWhiskey

node.text: When we bottle Michter's single barrel bourbons and ryes, we dump, filter, and bottle each barrel separately. Our production team does a variety of quality tests on every barrel to ensure that the whiskey always meets the Michter's quality standards.

node.text:
Bar Manager @alexmilik at @mrporter_official is bringing Kentucky to Amsterdam with his "Kentucky Berry" cocktail. 

Kentucky Berry
40ml Michter's US*1 Sour Mash
20ml Creme de Mure
20ml lemon juice
10ml homemade raspberry cordial
3 drops Magic Velvet foamer
Shake and fine strain

May your Friday look as good as this "Occidental Old Fashioned." Created by @otissf, bartender and co-owner of @theoccidentalcigarclub in San Francisco.

Occidental Old Fashioned
2 oz Michter's US*1 Bourbon
.25 oz demerrara sugar
.25 oz soda water 
1 dash Angostura bitters
1 dash Regan’s orange bitters
